articles.description: At BlizzCon 2023, Blizzard president Mike Ybarra talked to The Verge about Microsoft’s Activision Blizzard acquisition and the games it has in development.
articles.content: The dust is finally starting to settle from Microsofts huge acquisition of Activision Blizzard, but even Blizzard president Mike Ybarra still isnt exactly sure how things will change for the company.… [+6312 chars]
